  "instructions": [
    "Preheat your air fryer to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Rinse the pork loin and pat it dry with paper towels.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together the minced garlic, grated ginger, ground cumin, ground coriander, smoked paprika, flaky salt, and freshly ground pepper.",
    "Rub the spice mixture all over the pork loin, making sure to coat it evenly.",
    "Drizzle the cold-pressed olive oil over the pork loin and sprinkle with freshly squeezed lemon juice.",
    "Place the pork loin in the air fryer basket and cook for 20 minutes.",
    "After 20 minutes, baste the pork loin with the pan juices and continue cooking for another 10-12 minutes, or until it reaches an internal temperature of 145°F (63°C).",
    "Remove the pork loin from the air fryer and let it rest for 5-7 minutes before slicing and serving."
  ],
